<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Word Jumble</title>
    <script
      src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.0.0-beta1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
      integrity="sha384-ygbV9kiqUc6oa4msXn9868pTtWMgiQaeYH7/t7LECLbyPA2x65Kgf80OJFdroafW"
      crossorigin="anonymous"
    ></script>
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fondamento&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
    <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/css/style.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <button data-modal-target="#modal">Games Rules</button>
    <div class="modal" id="modal">
      <div class="modal-header">
        <div class="title">Game Rules</div>
        <button data-close-button class="close-button">&times;</button>
      </div>
      <div class="modal-body">
        The object of this game is to unscramble the generated words, which
        happen to be the 50 states within the USA. For each word that is
        correctly guessed, the user will receive 5 points. But, don't get
        stuck....because the game won't let you continue until you correctly
        guess the word. So......Good Luck and Happy Jumbling!
      </div>
    </div>
    <div id="overlay"></div>

    <header class="header1">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="banner-text">
          <div class="text-area">
            <span>W</span>
            <span>o</span>
            <span>r</span>
            <span>d</span>&nbsp;
            <span>J</span>
            <span>u</span>
            <span>m</span>
            <span>b</span>
            <span>l</span>
            <span>e</span>
          </div>

          <p>
            To get started, Please click the button below to Login or Register
          </p>

          <p class="banner-btn">
            <a href="/users/login">Get Started</a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </header>

    <footer><%- include('./partials/footer'); %></footer>
    <script defer src="/js/script.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.3.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.3/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.1.3/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
